title: Eden High Series 2 #5
description: After the explosion at Sian's home, Jace has some hard choices to make. He's lived his life as one of the crowd in a town where it's known that his family rules. But now to keep his girl safe, he's willing to give up his happy go lucky lifestyle and be the son he was meant to be. There will be some drastic changes at Eden High, and not everyone will be pleased...
author: Jordan Silver
